Celebrating 17 years of Mani Square mall! 🎉🎊🥳

What a blast we had! I felt like I went back to my childhood days when I visited the mall back in 2008. A fun filled day cutting an enormous cake, adda over Starbucks coffee,meet and greet and some lovely memorable pictures. 🎂

Thanks @paromita.candid  @sudarshanagangulee.
 for having me.❤️

And ofcourse, a special mention to all you lovely people who were there. What can I say, I felt lile I was celebrating my birthday with you all. You guys simply made my day. ❤️ I wish I could meet each one of you personally. Thank you! 🙏

🎥 @acinema95 ❤️
